        final long oldSize = cache.sizeInBytes();
        cache.evict();
        sizeInBytes.getAndAdd(cache.sizeInBytes() - oldSize);
    }
}
```
**Locks Object:** `this` (ThreadCache) then `cache` (NamedCache)
**Risk Level:** MEDIUM - Potential deadlock if another thread locks NamedCache then tries to lock ThreadCache

