public Optional<String> addStreamThread() {
    if (isRunningOrRebalancing()) {
        final StreamThread streamThread;
        synchronized (changeThreadCount) {  // Lock 1: changeThreadCount
            final int threadIdx = nextThreadIndex();
            final int numLiveThreads = numLiveStreamThreads();
            final long cacheSizePerThread = cacheSizePerThread(numLiveThreads + 1);
            resizeThreadCache(cacheSizePerThread);
            streamThread = createAndAddStreamThread(cacheSizePerThread, threadIdx);
        }
        synchronized (stateLock) {  // Lock 2: stateLock
            if (isRunningOrRebalancing()) {
                streamThread.start();
                return Optional.of(streamThread.getName());
            } else {
                // ... cleanup
            }
        }
    }
}
```
**Locks Objects:** `changeThreadCount` then `stateLock`
**Risk Level:** HIGH - Reverse lock ordering could occur if stateLock holder calls addStreamThread

